{
  "text": "This is the first randomised placebo-controlled clinical study for the treatment of SAD with ESC in Japan. Apart from this study, three clinical studies of ESC have been conducted in patients with SAD in countries outside of Japan. In these studies, the short-term (12 weeks) and long-term (24 weeks) efficacy of ESC treatment and relapse-prevention effect (24 weeks) were established, and its safety and tolerability were also demonstrated [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
